@1246 = ~Well then, would the master consider letting Cespenar use?  No?  Stingy, stingy...  what else you has then?~
@1247 = ~Oooohhhh!  The master has such good taste!  Cespenar loooves what you has done with this human flesh... though it not quite look finished....~
@1248 = ~I can finishes human skin-armor into something much wonderful for you master, I would just need an old lich robe... like maybe... Vecna's?  Oh and human flesh skin must be cured with bloods.  Dragon bloods...Shadow Dragon bloods to be specific for best result.  And don't forget the gold shinys! 10,000 to be precise!~
@1249 = ~Master is truly the great one if <PRO_HESHE> can gets ahold of both Vecna robe and nasty Shadow Dragon bloods. Shall loyal butler get to work on fixing up human skin-flesh for you?~
@1250 = ~Well, if the master isn't going to use human flesh-skin, can Cespenar use to make new coat?  Or maybe jerky-beef?  No?  Master is sooo stingy sometimes......~
@1251 = ~What now?  The master wants the Lich's Raiment improved even mores?~
@1252 = ~I dont know if I has... wait...wait.......maybe, just maybe.  Yes, I can makes it even better!  But Cespenar would need a relic of very dark magic... like a skull from a lich~
@1253 = ~The master is truly astounding... this is definitely an empowered lich's skull.  If the master can part with a measly sum of 10,000 golds, I will get to work on reforging human-skin-armor right away.~
@1254 = ~Truly?  Master, I would highly recommend using skull for ashtray then.  Teeths can hold all forms of smoke-device for you, trust me!  No messes for butler to clean!~
@1255 = ~What you has this time, Master?  Smells like moldy socks... but is sealed scroll?  Must be something reaallly important inside...~
@1256 = ~Very tricksy recipe to open sealed scroll, would needs some scaleses from stinky, evil dragon.  Red, blue, black, green, white, or shadow would do.~
@1257 = ~Cespenar can use dragon scales you has here to remove seal from musty old scroll.~
@1258 = ~I can uses these red dragon scales to unseal old scroll for you.~
@1259 = ~I can uses these shadow dragon scales to unseal old scroll for you.~
@1260 = ~I can uses these white dragon scales to unseal old scroll for you.~
@1261 = ~I can uses these blue dragon scales to unseal old scroll for you.~
@1262 = ~I can uses these green dragon scales to unseal old scroll for you.~
@1263 = ~I can uses these black dragon scales to unseal old scroll for you.~
@1264 = ~So many stinky scales from old nasty lizards, the master sure knows how to put those big bullies in their place!~
@1265 = ~I would just need stinky scales and 10,000 gold shinys.~
@1266 = ~No then?  Would master like to play tiddlywinks with scales instead?~
@1267 = ~Such shiny red blade this is, is red from blood of enemies?  Cespenar sure hopes so...~
@1268 = ~You would like for loyal butler to improves crimson blade for you?  I can do, but would need something most untasteful... gemstone of yucky light.~
@1269 = ~You has light-stone here, I can uses this with 5,000 gold shinys to improves crimson blade for you.~
@1270 = ~Okay then, no on crimson blade, what else you has for me to look at?~
@1271 = ~Ohhh, good balanced fighter-sword you have here master, you would likes it improved?~
@1272 = ~Loyal butler can improve fighter-sword for you, I would needs icky gemstone of light and 5,000 shiny golds.~
@1273 = ~You has the light gem here, and the golds, should I get to work on fighter-sword for you, master?~
@1274 = ~No then?  Do you have other shinys for me to look through?~
@1275 = ~Master would like red dawn-blade enhanced further?  Hmmm...  Might have a recipe for that.~
@1276 = ~To reforge dawn-blade, I will needs metal from sky, not sure how you would get that...~
@1277 = ~You found sky-metal!  I can use to enhance red katana for you, I just needs 10,000 golds for complete the recipe.~
@1278 = ~Oh alright then.. was looking forward to using sky-metal, never got to work with that before.  What else do you has for me?~
@1279 = ~You would likes your fighter-sword improved further?  That's a tought one, even for me....~
@1280 = ~Cespenar does have recipe, just one, needs star-metal ore to reforge sword for you.~
@1281 = ~You gots star-metal?  Did the master pluck it from the sky?   Well, since you has ore, I can use with 10,000 gold shinys to enhance fighter-sword for you.~
@1282 = ~No?  Shucks... well what else you has for me?~
