Speed Factor: 2
Proficiency Type: Long Sword
Type: One-handed
Requires:
 6 Strength

Weight: 2~
@2003 = ~Tongue of Burning Acid +4~
@2004 = ~After being reforged and enhanced with the fiery essence of Angurvadal, the blade of the Tongue of Acid is now engulfed in hellish green flames of acidic wrath.  Wounds caused by the blade sizzle and burn with acidic fire, causing crippling pain to any creature unfortunate enough to be struck by it.

