@2037 = ~Robe of Roaring Flames~
@2038 = ~Meticulously re-threaded and infused with the magics derived from Vecna's robe, Odesseiron's crimson garment has taken on an entirely new countenance, and now improves the wearer's casting speed while providing much improved protections.  If Edwin were to see what has become of his old robe, he would surely want it back with fervor.

